{
  "name": "@octaviocriollo/nocodb-mcp",
  "version": "0.3.0",
  "description": "NocoDB MCP server - 25 tools, fixed for NocoDB v2 API (2026+). Fork of andrewlwn77/nocodb-mcp with v1→v2 endpoint migration.",
